data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!!! Location! Just minutes from Lake Nona, Lakeshore Lake, and next to all the amenities of downtown St. Cloud. This Single-family home features a two Bedroom, two Full Baths, family room and spacious open floor plan with a gorgeous modern appeal. The kitchen, which overlooks the living area, comes with all stainless-steel appliances and granite counters. Spacious backyard for everyone in the family to enjoy. Close to Lakefront Park, playground, splash park, boat launch, walking trails, local favorite Crabby Bills, Orlando airport, shopping centers, restaurants and easy access to major highways. Schedule your private showing TODAY!! New Roof 2022.
